### List MCP prompts
# Prerequisite: run mcp_initialize.http and paste session id below.

POST http://localhost:8080/
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream
Mcp-Session-Id: PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 10,
  "method": "prompts/list",
  "params": {}
}
